title: Freshmen
description:
Fourteen college freshmen are cast out of the main dormitory and forced to live in temporary housing in the Boughl Science Building where they are given superhuman powers by the "ax-cell-erator" after an explosion. With powers based on whatever they were thinking at that pivotal moment, some of the kids are blessed with fantastic abilities, but others see their powers as a curse. Co-created by writer/producer/actor Seth Green (Robot Chicken, Family Guy) and Hugh Sterbakov. Published by Top Cow.



Released on http://ComicPirates.info
